Tunde Opalana, Abuja PDP governorship candidate in Isun State, Senator Ademola Adeleke has been reportedly arrested by security operatives and has since been detained.According to information from his media office, Adeleke was invited this afternoon by the police and upon reporting at the Maitama Police Station , Abuja, he was detained.Recall that the PDP recently raised the alarm of plots to arrest oand silence Adeleke.Details later.